To run the specs you need to install PHPSpec framework into your PHP Environment

To install PHPSpec you need PEAR installed, after install pear follow these instructions into your console (don't type sudo if you are running on Windows):

1. sudo pear upgrade PEAR
2. sudo pear channel-discover pear.phpspec.org
3. sudo pear install phpspec/PHPSpec

If all occur correctly you are now able to run the specs, go to spec folder of Fishy Framework into your console and run the following command:

phpspec -r

This will run all the tests